&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;TC2 for C99 (only the TC, not the standard incorporating it): &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.open-std.org/jtc1/sc22/wg14/www/docs/9899-1999_cor_2-2004.pdf&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;http://www.open-std.org/jtc1/sc22/wg14/www/docs/9899-1999_cor_2-2004.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
